title: Atkins Harvest Trail Bars
description:
When carb cravings hit, hit back with the new Atkins Harvest Trail Bars. It uses simple and nutritious ingredients that provide a good dose of protein and fiber while keeping net carbs and sugar levels in check.

Comes in 4 delicious flavors: Dark Chocolate Sea Salt Caramel, Dark Chocolate Peanut Butter, Vanilla Fruit & Nut, and Dark Chocolate Cherry & Nuts.
